boyfriend get wet and sick.

707
00:50:10,209 --> 00:50:11,542
Hey you.

708
00:50:12,042 --> 00:50:14,876
What kind of a man you intend 
to be?  A hypocrite?

709
00:50:15,125 --> 00:50:15,834
What!?

710
00:50:15,959 --> 00:50:18,501
