into a good person?

717
00:50:32,709 --> 00:50:34,918
You are disgusting.

718
00:50:38,918 --> 00:50:40,167
I see.

719
00:50:40,626 --> 00:50:43,626
It's natural you know what I did, 
hearing from Nishimiya.

720
00:50:44,918 --> 00:50:47,167
Yes.  You are right.

721
00:50:47,584 --> 00:50:49,667
