Yu-ju,

744
00:52:23,459 --> 00:52:24,834
Hey, sis!

745
00:52:24,959 --> 00:52:26,959
I'b zorry, I'b zorry!

746
00:52:27,334 --> 00:52:29,417
All right, no problem.

747
00:52:29,834 --> 00:52:30,626
Hey.

748
00:52:30,751 --> 00:52:33,459
