753
00:52:45,125 --> 00:52:46,918
Both I and sis.

754
00:52:49,000 --> 00:52:50,292
Hey boy!

755
00:52:50,417 --> 00:52:52,125
Nice to see you!

756
00:52:52,250 --> 00:52:53,584
