819
00:56:29,792 --> 00:56:31,375
Sho-chan?

820
00:56:31,501 --> 00:56:33,167
Sorry.

821
00:56:33,292 --> 00:56:34,417
Sho-chan!

822
00:56:35,834 --> 00:56:38,667
