823
00:56:38,876 --> 00:56:40,459
Do you remember me?

824
00:56:41,209 --> 00:56:42,918
Hello!

825
00:56:43,042 --> 00:56:45,125
Huh?  Ishida-kun?

826
00:56:46,375 --> 00:56:47,417
Heh heh heh.

827
00:56:48,167 --> 00:56:50,159
